                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Gaviarius <expan><abbr>aug</abbr><ex>ur</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>IIvir <expan><abbr>quinq</abbr><ex>uennalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urionum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>decr</abbr><ex>eto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mur</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ref</abbr><ex>iciendum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>coer</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>idemq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>prob</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich überliefert. Z. 1: überliefert ist: L. GAVI ARNN AVG. Z. 4: überliefert ist: IDEM Q PROB CORQ. (B): Sestieri: Z. 1: Arn(ensis?) aug(uris); Anamali - Ceka - Deniaux: Z. 1: Gavi(arius) aug(ur); Z. 2: duumvir.</p>
            </div>
